column5: 3,000 sf 2-story home located in The Woodlands, Texas, in nice suburban neighborhood, located minutes away from The Woodlands Mall & Market Street with plenty of restaurants and shopping. 35 minute commute to NRG Stadium. Quick access to I-45.  Kitchen is fully stocked with condiments, coffee pot, appliances, cookware, napkins and paper towels.
column8: Large Beautiful Home located in The Woodlands
